    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Biviis Trivi<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> Qu<lb break="no" n="3"/>adrivi<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> Satto<lb break="no" n="4"/>nius Iuvenilis <lb n="5"/>b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> pro sa<lb break="no" n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">l</supplied>ute sua et suor<lb break="no" n="7"/>um posuit <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Id</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Dec</abbr><ex>embribus</ex></expan> Gra<lb break="no" n="9"/>to et Seleuco co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Z. 3/4: Schallmayer, Mattern: S(extus) Antonius; Filtzinger: S(extus) Attonius; Z. 5/6: CIL: sa/[l]ute. Z. 8/9: Filtzinger, Ihm: Gra/[to et Seleuco co(n)s(ulibus)]; Günther: Gra/to et Seleuco [co(n)s(ulibus)]; Schallmayer, Mattern: Gra/[to et S]eleuco co(n)s(ulibus). Autopsie R. Wiegels.</p>
            </div>
